chival detail, this collection provides a wealth of interdisciplinary expertise on one of history's greatest intellectuals.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aBishopszSpainzSeville. 0aChristian literature, EarlyxLatin authorsxHistory and criticism. 0aFathers of the church. 4aEarly Middle Ages. 4aHistory. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh  aIsidore of Seville.  aSpain.  aVisigoths.  aearly medieval history.  alate antiquity.1 aBeagon, Mary, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCarlson, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDi Sciacca, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFear, Andrew, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFear, Andy, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFouracre, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeath, Christopher, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKelly, Michael J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMarkauskas, Melissa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSmyth, Marina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWood, Jamie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWood, Jamie, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package 2016-2018z978311066731808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package Backlist 2015-2017z978311060644708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015z978311070064040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048526765zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://